    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows expected signs of age and use. Mechanically, the engine starts reliably and the car handles well, but you should anticipate some upcoming maintenance, such as a brake pad replacement and a minor oil leak that will eventually need attention. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows some upholstery wear and a non-functional rear window motor. It is a solid, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections and minor repairs.",
