      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for this absolute gem! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and still runs like a dream. It's in really nice shape and is totally ready for your next road trip or daily commute. I've honestly loved every mile in this car, and I know you will too! It\u2019s solid, comfortable, and waiting for a new owner to take it on some adventures. Drop me a message if you want to come see it\u2014I'd love to show you around!",
